{"tid":615201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋人工島防波堤疑被沖散 網民憂行車安全","createTime":"2018-04-03T07:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T08:10:18.000Z","uid":37554,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60f9228cc4251f99d701c91b4cfb165ad48dd179","tid":615201,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"如火如荼趕工中的港珠澳大橋工程又起風波！有網民近日以航拍機拍攝港珠澳大橋其中一個「海底隧道出入口人工島」時，意外攝得人工島其中一邊由大石組成的防波堤邊界，如狗牙般凹凸不平，懷疑大量防波堤大石疑被沖散（沖落海）。網民對事件議論紛紛，有人擔心工程不安全，有人更憂慮人工島會移位，甚至擔心行車隧道會入水。<br />\n<br />\n有留言者讚嘆拍攝者的相片揭露港珠澳大橋工程的真相，但亦有人笑稱恐怕拍攝者會被指泄露國家機密。上述防波堤的問題相信更已出現多時。因去年7月內地官媒曾刊出港珠港大橋的施工情況情況，當時其中兩相片已見到海底隧道東、西入口人工島的海堤邊緣不齊整，《蘋果》把有關相片與今次的航拍相片比，估計航拍中拍攝的是比較接近香港一邊的海底隧道東入口人工島。<br />\n整個港珠澳大橋共有4個人工島，包括香港口岸人工島、珠澳口岸人工島以及海底隧道東、西出入口人工島。但貼圖的航拍者，並無講明它所拍攝的是的海底隧道「東出入口」還是「西出入口」人工島。<br />\n<br />\n香港只負責興建香港口岸人工島，但該人工島在趕工下亦屢生問題，包括填海用的大圓筒出現急速沉降事故。至於另外3個人工島的工程則由珠海及澳門兩地負責。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180403/large/1522733873_9b3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180403%2Flarge%2F1522733873_9b3f.jpg&h=0ff9cb05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b20eab371c7b752417dc665d473aa8fe493e9ad","tid":615201,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180403/58028522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F58028522&d=P4b8p5DmM7BDUOa8YOsbhARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=005b5d9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F58028522&h=2b1ee6b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180403/58028522</a>"},{"pid":"8936682a75e6aef3bd8451dc54a5dbe689e4b75f","tid":615201,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"呢個石屎建築物可能頂唔到10年<br />\n比佢預設咁高強度既應有既過百年咪少左9成<br />\n120年入面可以重修十次<br />\n<br />\ngdp仲唔昇昇昇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國承建商肥肥囉<br />\n香港新興永續性reboot civil工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf7541e8eb180a8d31f60f12aca1ea2304f546c","tid":615201,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e53795e2133d91e070c3edce9c24b205e446a22","tid":615201,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"揸揸下車變潛艇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf62b14d313c5aa007416d533b0b718cfa815b26","tid":615201,"uid":55511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"好想睇條橋收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a9876a1b8cbdb71a2d1178e0aec3a840947bb2","tid":615201,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"十號風球 幾米高嘅浪 頂唔頂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}